<h1 class="docs-header">Image Classes</h1>
<p>Alignment modifiers are classes for images that help position them within the context of a document. There are also a few stylistic modifiers for commonly used image effects.</p>

<ul class="docs-list">
  
  <li>
    <h2 class="docs-header">.align-left</h2>
    <p>Floats an image to the left and adds top, right and bottom margins so that text wraps around the image properly.</p>
    <pre class="language-markup"><code>&lt;img class=&quot;align-left&quot; src=&quot;...&quot;&gt;</code></pre>
    <div class="demo">
      <img class="align-left" alt="Placeholder image" src="http://placehold.it/150x150">
    </div>
  </li>
  
  <li>
    <h2 class="docs-header">.align-center</h2>
    <p>Centers an image by making it block and giving it left and right margins of <code>auto</code>.</p>
    <pre class="language-markup"><code>&lt;img class=&quot;align-center&quot; src=&quot;...&quot;&gt;</code></pre>
    <div class="demo">
      <img class="align-center" alt="Placeholder image" src="http://placehold.it/150x150">
    </div>
  </li>
  
  <li>
    <h2 class="docs-header">.align-right</h2>
    <p>Floats an image to the right and adds top, left and bottom margins so that text wraps around the image properly.</p>
    <pre class="language-markup"><code>&lt;img class=&quot;align-right&quot; src=&quot;...&quot;&gt;</code></pre>
    <div class="demo">
      <img class="align-right" alt="Placeholder image" src="http://placehold.it/150x150">
    </div>
  </li>
  
  <li>
    <h2 class="docs-header">.img-rounded</h2>
    <p>Adds rounded border radius based on the default border-radius setting <code>$border-radius</code>.</p>
    <pre class="language-markup"><code>&lt;img class=&quot;img-rounded&quot; src=&quot;...&quot;&gt;</code></pre>
    <div class="demo">
      <img class="align-center img-rounded" alt="Placeholder image" src="http://placehold.it/150x150">
    </div>
  </li>
  
  <li>
    <h2 class="docs-header">.img-circle</h2>
    <p>Makes a circle effect on an image by adding <code>50%</code> border radius.</p>
    <pre class="language-markup"><code>&lt;img class=&quot;img-circle&quot; src=&quot;...&quot;&gt;</code></pre>
    <div class="demo">
      <img class="align-center img-circle" alt="Placeholder image" src="http://placehold.it/150x150">
    </div>
  </li>
  
  <li>
    <h2 class="docs-header">.img-polaroid</h2>
    <p>Adds a polaroid effect to an image.</p>
    <pre class="language-markup"><code>&lt;img class=&quot;img-polaroid&quot; src=&quot;...&quot;&gt;</code></pre>
    <div class="demo">
      <img class="align-center img-polaroid" alt="Placeholder image" src="http://placehold.it/150x150">
    </div>
  </li>
  
</ul>
</section>
